description:
An SD Gunpla in which the F-Kunoichi that http://anidb.net/ch95325 [Ayame] previously used is recreated with a Cross Silhouette structure. Its equipment has been thoroughly updated, and her newest Ayame Ninja Techniques are also very effective when unleashed by a machine that specializes in shape-shifting abilities.
Source: Official page
name: F-Kunoichi Kai
